Name: version_hunter
Version: 1.0
Summary: Command line versioning helper for Cx_Freeze / Inno Setup builds.
Home-page: https://github.com/Tomasz-Kluczkowski/versioner
Author: Tomasz Kluczkowski
Author-email: tomaszk1@hotmail.co.uk
License: MIT
Description: VERSIONING HELPER FOR CX_FREEZE BUILDS (AND NOT ONLY)
        
        The goal of this program is to provide an easy way to implement version changes when building an application using cx_Freeze / Inno Setup. All you need in the most basic situation is a version file in the root of your project directory.
Platform: UNKNOWN
